data.description: Hard to find 4 bedroom, 2 full bathroom house in Iroquois School District with tons of upgrades and a modern farmhouse aesthetic! Property backs up to Buffalo Creek and also includes a second lot. This home has been meticulously maintained and some major updates include new tear off roof in 2020, new siding plus new vinyl and glass block windows. Heated above ground pool with expansive 2-level deck is grilling and pool party ready. Very large blacktop driveway to accomodate whatever you may have. Downstairs has a large den as well as a bonus room currently being used as a 5th bedroom. Separate laundry room with granite countertop, sink and new cabinets. All matching Luxury vinyl plank waterproof flooring on both levels lets the rooms flow into each other nicely and are great for kids and pets. Large attached 2 car garage and shed provides tons of storage. Well manicured and low maintenance perennial landscaping surrounds this home which sits on almost 3 acres. Kitchen has been updated with new cabinets, granite, sink and appliances as well as custom open shelving. This home is ready for a family that likes to be active, entertain and enjoys the outdoors! Move in ready!
